des:
Manage your Tinker Federal Credit Union account with Alexa. Using your Amazon Alexa device, you can now check balances, transfer money, make loan payments, and much more. Tinker Federal Credit Union is proud to provide members with the most convenient ways to access their accounts, anytime, anywhere. Please keep in mind that your financial information may be read aloud or displayed visually after you have provided your personal pin.
